So it was the work of the horse that identified Alfonso Cano's body.
A lobbyist from Cali went into history as the man who confirmed the death of "Alfonso Cano".
The work of these officials is key.
Last November 4, a lobbyist from Cali's ITC went on to history as the man who confirmed the identity of the Farc's top chief: "Alfonso Cano", through the collage of his fingerprints.
Of the seven lophoscopists working in the ITC sectional, that week was the turn of "availability" to Eliazar González, a man from Puerto Tejada who has been working in the area of judicial investigation for 21 years.
When he began his career, González worked in the municipalities of Chocó, where he often had to go into the jungle for more than five days to get to the place where the bodies were to be identified.
In 2000 he moved to the capital of the Valley and, after taking the corresponding courses, he specialized in lophoscopia, which is the study of the skin of friction, that is, the palms of the hands and feet.
The week of operation against alias Alfonso Cano to Eliazar warned him to wear minimum clothes for three days.
Something big was waiting for him.
On Friday night he left for the Cauca in a helicopter from Palmira.
He knew that he had to identify two bodies and that one of them was suspected of being the man who was leading the oldest guerrilla in the world, so he was asked to carry Guillermo León Sáenz's decactilary card (his real name).
However, when he arrived with the investigation team at the site where the body was located, he did not recognize him because of his physical appearance, as he was very different from what he had seen in the media.
He was without a beard, dressed like a local farmer, no glasses and much thinner.
But the prints don't lie.
Accompanied by a galtonian magnifying glass, ink, a transplanter and a flashlight, Eliazar compared the fingerprints of the body with those of the card.
His eye didn't fail him: it was "Alfonso Cano".
That same night, the man from Puerto Tejada was in charge of confirming to the Minister of Defense, Juan Carlos Pinzón, that he was the chief of the Farcs.
In search of the footprint
For a Dactiloscopist from the Sijín de Cali the recognition that President Juan Manuel Santos made to Eliazar González, in the press conference for the operation against "Cano", is very significant.
A lot of people don't know our work.
Dactyloscopy is an exact science, without margin of error, that can become key in the resolution of crimes.
Apart from the identification of corpses, lophoscopists support investigations into crimes such as theft and murder and confirm the identity of the captured persons.
When captured, many criminals present false ballots or have no papers.
We take the fingerprint and search them in the database.
The investigator said that, in a case of theft, he touched to remove a piece of wall from a house, for in that place the thief had supported his hand to take out a safe full of jewels and money.
"The walls are difficult because they are not suitable surfaces to draw a fingerprint, but in that case we were able to get the print of the whole hand and identify the offender, who had participated in different thefts," he recalled.
Fingerprints can also rule out or reaffirm suspects in homicide cases.
They recently found a dead man, with bottles of liquor around him.
The investigation determined that a relative could be suspected of the crime and, indeed, a print on the bottle coincided.
Although this doesn't guarantee it was the killer, it does place it at the crime scene.
A CTI dactiloscope explained that in objects "fingerprints are taken with chemical or physical reagents".
When they appear, a transplanter or tape is used to lift them.
After this, the impressions are sent to the Asif, which is the criminal database, or to the Registry.
"The problem is that there are still many undocumented Colombians," CTI expert said.
He clarified that not everything is as shown on the CSI television program.
Just as not everything that shines is gold, not everything that you touch becomes footprint.
However, if it can be used, if the respective check is made.
